Fingers crossed.Just for reference  the Sky Ark Chronicles telegram channel has 18.5k users.PS: Could mm2 asia sudden rally today be due to this? I guess only time can tell.

I think Vividthree will be a worthy punt at current prices. $0.042/$0.043 looks too bottomish here  considering that insiders did deal at $0.08x /. The last placement for VV3 was at $0.058x too.They announced recently that Crypto/Metaverseguy Jonathan Zhang has taken up executive role and he will be in charge of fund raising in coming months. Hence  hoping this is a placement deal at a price closer to last placement. Last round placement deal  they gapped up at least 15 pips from what i could recall.
